'''土壤'''（{{lang-de|'''Boden'''}}，{{lang-en|'''soil'''}}）是一種自然體，由數層不同厚度的土層（{{lang-de|Bodenhorizont}}，{{lang-en|soil horizon}}）所構成，主要成分是[[礦物質|礦物質]]。<ref name=Engel>{{cite book | last = Engel | first = Jens | authorlink =  | coauthors =  Lauer, Carsten | title = Einführung in die Boden- und Felsmechanik: Grundlagen und Berechnungen |year=2010 | publisher = Carl Hanser Verlag GmbH & Co. KG | location = München, Deutschland | isbn = 978-3-446-41461-7}}</ref>土壤和[[母質|母質]]（岩石）的差異主要是表現在[[形態特徵|形態特徵]]或[[物理|物理]]、[[化學|化學]]、[[礦物|礦物]]等<ref>Birkeland, Peter W. ''Soils and Geomorphology, 3rd Edition''. New York: Oxford University Press, 1999.</ref>。但這種解釋嚴格來說（或者以環境科學的角度來說）並不正確：土壤是由母質經過[[風化作用|風化作用]]後所形成的，其特性與母質不盡相同。<ref name="Chesworth2008">{{Citation| last = Chesworth | first =  Edited by Ward| year = 2008| title = Encyclopedia of soil science| pages = xxiv | isbn = 1402039948| publisher = Springer| location = Dordrecht, Netherland| nopp = true}}</ref>

土壤是各種[[風化作用|風化作用]]和生物的活動產生的礦物和有機物混合組成，存在著[[固體|固體]]、[[氣體|氣體]]及[[液體|液體]]等[[物態變化|狀態]]。<ref>Voroney, R. P., 2006. The Soil Habitat ''in'' Soil Microbiology, Ecology and Biochemistry, Eldor A. Paul ed.  ISBN=0125468075</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.columbia.edu/itc/cerc/seeu/atlantic/restrict/modules/module10_content.html |title=James A. Danoff-Burg, Columbia University The Terrestrial Influence: Geology and Soils |accessdate=2009-06-16 |archive-date=2009-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090217132023/http://www.columbia.edu/itc/cerc/seeu/atlantic/restrict/modules/module10_content.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>疏鬆的土壤微粒組合起來，形成充滿間隙的土壤，而在這些孔隙中則含有[[溶解溶液|溶解溶液]]（液體）和[[空氣|空氣]]（氣體）。<ref>Taylor, S. A., and G. L. Ashcroft. 1972. Physical Edaphology</ref>因此土壤通常被視為有三種狀態。<ref>McCarty, David. 1982. Essentials of Soil Mechanics and Foundations</ref>大部分土壤的[[密度|密度]]為1～2 g/cm³。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pedosphere.com/resources/bulkdensity/triangle_us.cfm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-06-16 |archive-date=2017-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171027084043/http://www.pedosphere.com/resources/bulkdensity/triangle_us.cfm |dead-url=no }}</ref>地球上大多數的土壤，生成時間多晚於[[更新世|更新世]]，只有很少的土壤成分的生成年代早於[[第三紀|第三紀]]。<ref name=Buol73>{{cite book | last = Buol | first = S. W. | authorlink =  | coauthors = Hole, F. D. and McCracken, R. J. | title = Soil Genesis and Classification | url = https://archive.org/details/soilgenesisclass02edbuol | edition = First |year=1973 | publisher = Iowa State University Press | location = Ames, IA | isbn = 0-8138-1460-X}}.</ref>
